<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>That rude boys Community Landing Page</title>

    <style>

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }


        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }


        .top-nav-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 60px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .nav-links ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #007bff;
        }


        .first-section {
            background-color: #f4f7fe;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 80px 60px;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .introduction {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        .introduction h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .hero-image-placeholder {
            flex: 1;
            height: 300px;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #718096;
        }


        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #cbd5e1;
        }


        .about-us-section {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }


        .content-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 60px 60px;
            gap: 50px;
        }

        .content-row.reverse {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        .content-text {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .content-image {
            flex: 1;
            height: 250px;
            background-color: #edf2f7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #a0aec0;
        }


        .blue-banner-section {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .blue-banner-section h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }


        .contact-form-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .form-container {
            max-width: 450px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .form-container input, .form-container textarea {
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .form-container button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .form-container button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="top-nav-bar">
            <h1>Help-Everyone</h1>
            <nav class="nav-links">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#donate">Donate</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#who-we-are">Who we are</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#join-us">Join us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>

        <section class="first-section">
            <div class="introduction">
                <h1>We Help Everyone Here For A Better Life</h1>
                <p>If you like helping others, get started with us today.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
                    <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">Watch our story</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image-placeholder">Figma Hero Image Graphic</div>
        </section>


        <section id="who-we-are" class="about-us-section">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Dedicated to building stronger, more supportive communities worldwide by providing direct resources to individual programs.</p>
        </section>


        <section id="services" class="services-block">
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-text">
                    <h2>Our Services</h2>
                    <p>Connecting people with local volunteer opportunities to create lasting change across families.</p>
                    <a href="#">About this &rarr;</a>
                </div>
                <div class="content-image">Service Illustration</div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-row reverse">
                <div class="content-text">
                    <h2>Resource Distribution</h2>
                    <p>Providing essential tools and transparent funding pathways directly to local neighborhood initiatives.</p>
                    <a href="#">About this &rarr;</a>
                </div>
                <div class="content-image">Distribution Illustration</div>
            </div>
        </section>


        <section id="donate" class="blue-banner-section">
            <h2>Ready to transform a neighborhood today?</h2>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary" style="background-color: #fff; color: #007bff;">Join Our Mission</a>
        </section>


        <section id="contact" class="contact-form-section">
            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Leave your information below and our tracking coordinators will reach out.</p>
            <div class="form-container">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email Address" required>
                <textarea placeholder="How would you like to help?" rows="4" required></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Submit Form</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

</body>
</html>

